clips\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s most overwhelming sporting event to follow.\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 218}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 236}, {\"ngram\": \"most overwhelming sporting event\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike March Madness or the World Cup, there are dozens of different sports, countless rules to familiarize yourself with and the possibility of being fully entranced by an event you can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t quite remember if you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve ever seen before.\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"March Madness\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 301}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"different sports\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"countless rules\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This summer in Paris they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll hand out medals in 329 events across 39 sports.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.3466142067541764e-28, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"329 events\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"39 sports\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t watch all of them\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094tho